steps.name: When the user provides valid credentials to sign in
Then User should click in sigin button
When Mouse hover on user profile section
When Seller will click on Storefront from profile menu

Then Seller should redirect to create listing page
When Seller fills all the required details about the product and saves the details

steps.name: Then Seller should navigate to Inventory and Pricing page
When Seller Uploads Image and fillup the Inventory, Pricing details
Then Seller should navigate to Shipping and Returns page
When Seller fills all Shipping and Return detail and save the details
Then Seller should navigate to product listing confirmation page
When Seller publish the product details from listing confirmation page
Then Seller should display confirm submission popup
When Seller clicks on go to listing management button
Then Seller should navigate to the Listing Management page and verifies product is listed
